    <ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
        <defName>HP_Gun_PlasmaGun</defName>
        <label>plasma gun</label>
        <description>In the Warhammer 40,000 universe, the Plasma Gun is a powerful and versatile energy weapon employed by various factions, including the Adeptus Astartes (Space Marines) and other forces within the Imperium of Man.\n\nThe Plasma Gun operates by harnessing and superheating a gas or plasma charge within its chamber before expelling it as a searing bolt of energy. Upon impact, the superheated plasma inflicts devastating damage, capable of melting through armor and causing explosive harm to targets.\n\nWhile extremely potent, Plasma Guns come with a degree of risk due to the volatility of the plasma they discharge. Overheating or misfiring can lead to catastrophic consequences for the user, potentially resulting in dangerous explosions.\n\nHowever, the weapon's effectiveness against armored foes and its ability to deliver powerful shots at medium to close range make it a favored choice among elite infantry units and specialists operating within the grim and unrelenting conflicts of the Warhammer 40,000 universe.</description>
        <techLevel>Spacer</techLevel>
        <graphicData>
            <drawSize>1.2</drawSize>
            <texPath>Things/Weapons/Ranged/PlasmaGun</texPath>
            <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
        </graphicData>
        <soundInteract>Interact_ChargeRifle</soundInteract>
        <statBases>
            <WorkToMake>38000</WorkToMake>
            <Mass>5.5</Mass>
            <AccuracyTouch>0.90</AccuracyTouch>
